snippet.title: The Enchanted Turnabout [FT] Part 1: Into The Woods, To Get That Bread-
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty First-Time Playthrough]

A trip to Labyrinthia! Is this the closest I'm going to come to playing the PL vs AA game on this channel? Maybe-

But alas, this is a game that takes place in Labyrinthia, the same universe as that game, with a twist and a very clear timeline AU-

Just what is going on in this lonely little house in the woods? Are the sins of the Landlord inherited by her daughters? Who is the witch afoot in the night here?
-----------------------------------------
The Enchanted Turnabout, by Ana! (Hexepta creator!)

In the middle of the woods, on a long stormy night, lies a house. Seven people. And among them, an ominous cackle.

(Contains light spoilers for Professor Layton VS Phoenix Wright. It's recommended you play that before playing this. However, as this case is set in an alternate universe, it does not directly spoil the plot of the game.)

Find it on Court Records here! https://www.forums.court-records.net/viewtopic.php?f=36&t=33004
